GaugeEngine: XML based file format storing a description (theme) to build
the gauges.  The GaugeEngine is intended to give photo-realisitic gauges
comparable to what you could buy off the shelf..  Will be based on the 
gnome canvas...

support for MS-II (difficult, requires parser to be designed and written to
handler it's I/O stream (different size variabels not layed out on clean
coundaries, makes it a bitch to deal with..)

